             were indicted for <rs id="t18220911-35-off186" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18220911-35-off186" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18220911-35-off186" type="offenceSubcategory" value="animalTheft"></interp>
               stealing, on the <rs id="t18220911-35-cd187" type="crimeDate">27th of August</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18220911-35-off186 t18220911-35-cd187"></join>, four live pigs, price 4 l. and one live sow, price 1 l.
            </rs> the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t18220911-35-victim342" type="victimName">
                     William 
                     Rhodes
                  <interp inst="t18220911-35-victim342" type="surname" value="Rhodes"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18220911-35-victim342" type="given" value="William"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18220911-35-victim342" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
